## make-fab

# Make FAB - Floating Action Button Wrapper Generator

## TRIGGER
"make a fab", "make this into a fab", "turn this into a fab", "create a fab", "wrap this in a fab"

## PURPOSE
Automates FAB Collection library creation - wraps HTML content in self-contained FAB infrastructure, generates deployment files, and provides S3 upload commands.

## WHAT IT DOES
- Prompts for: FAB name (kebab-case), Tabler icon, color, tooltip, HTML source
- Generates: {fab-name}.js (with embedded FAB Manager), test page, S3 commands
- Pattern: Self-contained library, single script tag deployment
- Output: Circular button in bottom-right that opens sidebar panel

## FULL IMPLEMENTATION
When trigger detected, read complete implementation:
```powershell
$content = Get-Content "C:/Users/mike.ullman/OneDrive - Vizio, Inc/Documents/Cline/Rules/full/make-fab.md" -Raw
```

Or use read_file tool:
`full/make-fab.md`

## QUICK REFERENCE
- **Validation:** Kebab-case names, hex colors, Tabler icons
- **Content strategies:** Inline (<500 chars), separate HTML file (>500 chars), URL
- **FAB Manager:** Embedded in each library (DRIFT WARNING pattern)
- **Coordination:** Multiple FABs coexist, hide when sidebar opens
- **Deployment:** S3 bucket `vizio-data-ingestion-resources/other/fabs/`


